<h2 id="topics-of-the-course">Topics of the course</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Basic notions</li>
  <li>Trees</li>
  <li>Connectivity</li>
  <li>Eulerian and Hamiltonian cycles</li>
  <li>Matchings</li>
  <li>Planar graphs</li>
  <li>Graph colourings</li>
  <li>The matrix tree theorem</li>
  <li>Kuratowskiâ€™s theorem</li>
  <li>Ramsey theory</li>
  <li>Extremal problems</li>
</ul>

